    "我向前一步，给他最后一个告别吻，唇齿相依片刻，心里半期待着他会让我留下。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/bai9.rpy:194
translate chinese bai9menu_99b0804b:

    # "But he doesn't. Not ready yet, I guess. So I pull away."
    "但他没有。大概还没准备好吧。于是我松开了他。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/bai9.rpy:197
translate chinese bai9menu_996630df:

    # bai "Bye, [pcname]."
    bai "再见，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/bai9.rpy:198
translate chinese bai9menu_2de26655:

    # pc "Bye, Bai."
    pc "再见，白。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/bai9.rpy:201
translate chinese bai9menu_3f5af290:

    # "With that, I leave his apartment and walk back to my car."
    "说完，我走出他的公寓，走向自己的车。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/bai9.rpy:202
translate chinese bai9menu_fab7459a:

    # "That was a fun evening."
    "真是个愉快的夜晚。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/bai9.rpy:221
translate chinese bai9end_87193ebc:

    # pc "I'm sorry, I can't. I'm not into this."
    pc "对不起，我不能。我对这种事没兴趣。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/bai9.rpy:222
translate chinese bai9end_28261d04:

    # bai "Oh, Okay. That's okay, I understand."
    bai "哦，好的。没关系，我理解。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/bai9.rpy:223
translate chinese bai9end_511bbc2a:

    # "I stand up and leave Bai's apartment. This just wasn't going to work for me."
    "我站起身，离开了Bai的公寓。这对我来说行不通。"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Bai/bai9.rpy:6
    old "You need to have your first kiss with Bai, which can happen at the end of a good date, if you haven't told him you were just friends."
    new "你需要和Bai完成初吻，这通常发生在一次愉快的约会结束时——前提是你还没告诉他你们只是朋友。"

    # game/Scenes/Bai/bai9.rpy:7
    old "After this, Bai will call you and invite you over in the evening sometime."
    new "之后，白会给你打电话，邀请你晚上去他家。"

    # game/Scenes/Bai/bai9.rpy:101
    old "No, I can't do this"
    new "不，我做不到"

    # game/Scenes/Bai/bai9.rpy:115
    old "I thought I could, but I can't do this"
    new "我以为我能行，但我做不到"

    # game/Scenes/Bai/bai9.rpy:126
    old "Yeah, please do"
    new "嗯，请务必去"

    # game/Scenes/Bai/bai9.rpy:163
    old "Want me to do you too?"
    new "要我帮你吗？"

    # game/Scenes/Bai/bai9.rpy:172
    old "Sure, let's watch another movie"
    new "当然，再看一部电影吧"

    # game/Scenes/Bai/bai9.rpy:185
    old "I better head home"
    new "我还是回家吧"

